"{\"uid\": \"kyivindependent.com-ukrainian-womens-saber-fencing-team-advances-to-semi-finals-at-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Ukraine's women's saber fencing team secured a path to the semi-finals at the Paris 2024 Olympics on Aug. 3, winning over Italy with a score of 45-37.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 7, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5139813431490144e-12, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the 38-minute match, Ukraine's 15-time world championship medalist Olga Kharlan, as well as fencers Olena Kravatska and Alina Komashchuk, will compete against Japan in the semi-finals at 3:20 p.m. Paris time on Aug. 3.\", \"from\": 152, \"to\": 376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 179, \"end\": 186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5139813431490144e-12, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 225, \"end\": 237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olha_Kharlan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olga Kharlan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olha_Kharlan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olha_Kharlan\"}, {\"begin\": 258, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elena_of_Moldavia\", \"score\": 0.999999986155217, \"rank\": 1.3844926836455419e-08, \"text\": \"Olena\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elena_of_Moldavia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elena_of_Moldavia\"}, {\"begin\": 278, \"end\": 294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alina_Komashchuk\", \"score\": 0.9999998289158758, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alina Komashchuk\", 