ames.\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Khyzhniak has secured a spot in the semifinals, guaranteeing him at least a bronze medal, as theOlympicregulations stipulate that there is no third-place match.\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ukraine has so far won two medals at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 1005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 952, \"end\": 959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5139813431490144e-12, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ShooterSerhiy Kulishwon a silver medal in the 50m rifle three-position event.\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are the news team of the Kyiv Independent.\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1113, \"end\": 1117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyiv\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3731471132858344e-17, \"text\": \"Kyiv\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyiv\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyiv\"}, {\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_politician\", \"score\": 0.7411955454473023, \"rank\": 0.34917162674743896, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_politician\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_politician\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are here to make sure our readers get quick, essential updates about the events in Ukraine.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1225, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1217, \"end\": 1224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5139813431490144e-12, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrain